QA report v2 P0 fixes:

BUG-01 — Stock Sheet React Error #31 STILL crashing:
  Root cause confirmed: ErrorBoundary in 0108 only wrapped the BODY.
  The header quote block (lines 682-696) renders OUTSIDE the boundary,
  so crashes bubble up past it.

  THREE-LAYER FIX:
  a) Sanitize localStorage state on load — coerce any non-string evidence
     to string (in case earlier autoPrefill poisoned a save with an object)
  b) Wrap ENTIRE return in StockSheetErrorBoundary (not just body)
  c) Defensive 'typeof ans?.evidence === string' on the input value prop

BUG-NEW-01/02 — Re-rating Margin/Multiple Expansion empty even with 25 MB stocks:
  Root cause: screeners only read /api/market/earnings-scan which has no data
  for small/mid Indian caps. User has 25 stocks in mb_excel_scored_v2
  localStorage with FULL opm/opmPrev/pe/peg/epsGrowth/accelSignal data
  ready to use.

  FIX:
  + readMultibaggerStocks() reads mb_excel_scored_v2 JSON parsing the
    ExcelRow[] structure with all financial fields
  + computeMarginExpansionFromMB(stocks) — qualifies if ANY of:
      opm > opmPrev (YoY margin expansion)
      opmExpansion > 0 (3yr expansion)
      accelSignal === 'ACCELERATING'
      profitAcceleration > 0
  + computeMultipleExpansionFromMB(stocks) — qualifies if:
      pe > 0 && pe < 200
      epsGrowth > 0 (any of epsGrowth / yoyProfitGrowth / profitCagr)
      peg < 5 (or compute from pe/epsGrowth if not given)
  + Sort by decreasing margin delta / increasing PEG
  + MERGE with API-derived rows (MB primary, API fills gaps)

BUG-NEW-03 — Model Shift false positives (NTPC, EPC, KPI):
  Root cause: ANY keyword in ANY article triggered model shift —
  'EPC' as contract type, 'NTPC' as PSU utility, 'KPI' as company name.

  FIX:
  + MODEL_SHIFT_TICKER_BLACKLIST: EPC / MW / GW / IPO / DAE / NTPC / NHPC /
    POWERGRID / COALINDIA / RELIANCE / TCS / INFY / WIPRO / HCLTECH
    (utilities + acronyms that AREN'T model-shifting)
  + MODEL_SHIFT_VERB_NEARBY: require model-shift VERB in same text
    ('transitioning to / pivots to / launches subscription / moves to
     recurring / business model shift / ARR reaches X'). Mere keyword
    presence not enough.

BUG-08 — Universe counter '(1)':
  FIX: format 'Multibagger Upload · N stocks' (was 'multibagger (1)').
  Same for portfolio / watchlist / NSE 500 / custom labels.

